that dreams are the opposite of reality?

9
00:01:18,011 --> 00:01:19,712
Hey, Lai.

10
00:01:22,048 --> 00:01:23,617
Are you asleep?

11
00:01:23,617 --> 00:01:25,385
Just about to go to sleep.

12
00:01:25,385 --> 00:01:26,853
What's up?

13
00:01:31,658 --> 00:01:33,560
Tell me something.

14
00:01:36,896 --> 00:01:39,584
Is it too late for me to pursue Gu Jin?

15
00:01:42,035 --> 00:01:43,360
Is it?

16
00:01:45,438 --> 00:01:46,840
But I can wait.

17
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,736
I don't want him to disappear.

18
00:01:59,652 --> 00:02:01,087
Go ahead.

19
00:02:01,087 --> 00:02:02,555
There is a medical term

20
00:02:02,555 --> 00:02:03,690
called cherophobia,

21
00:02:03,690 --> 00:02:05,859
fear of happiness syndrome.

22
00:02:06,392 --> 00:02:07,694
The patient's first reaction
when happiness arrives

23
00:02:07,694 --> 00:02:09,829
is to reject and escape,

24
00:02:09,829 --> 00:02:11,331
because in their subconscious,

25
00:02:11,331 --> 00:02:13,333
they believe that after extreme happiness,

26
00:02:13,333 --> 00:02:15,488
pain and sorrow will certainly follow.

27
00:02:21,174 --> 00:02:22,575
Wait.

28
00:02:22,575 --> 00:02:25,044
When did you become so clever?

29
00:02:26,146 --> 00:02:28,615
Did you see Gu Jin's mom

30
00:02:28,615 --> 00:02:30,950
who was desperately extorting money?

31
00:02:30,950 --> 00:02:33,620
Could it be that Boss Gu is afraid
that his mom will latch onto you,

32
00:02:33,620 --> 00:02:35,522
that he would hold you back

33
00:02:35,522 --> 00:02:37,757
that he couldn't make you happy?

34
00:02:40,226 --> 00:02:42,095
Yes, that should be correct.

35
00:02:42,095 --> 00:02:44,197
Would you pull away

36
00:02:44,197 --> 00:02:45,465
for such a foolish reason?

37
00:02:45,465 --> 00:02:47,167
Of course not.

38
00:02:47,167 --> 00:02:48,935
That's right.

39
00:02:49,636 --> 00:02:52,505
I heard from Ren
that today is Gu Jin's birthday.

40
00:02:52,505 --> 00:02:53,873
Poor guy.

41
00:02:53,873 --> 00:02:55,575
Having this kind of drama on a birthday

42
00:02:55,575 --> 00:02:57,210
