69
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:41,312
Sometimes a bit silly,

70
00:05:43,443 --> 00:05:44,800
but in a cute way.

71
00:05:47,914 --> 00:05:49,120
You are always very hardworking,

72
00:05:50,850 --> 00:05:53,888
whether it's writing novels, folding paper,

73
00:05:56,356 --> 00:05:57,568
or being in a relationship.

74
00:06:04,564 --> 00:06:06,208
I feel very comfortable with you,

75
00:06:08,034 --> 00:06:09,728
