83
00:06:41,334 --> 00:06:42,969
What's not good about you?

84
00:06:42,969 --> 00:06:44,370
You're handsome.

85
00:06:44,370 --> 00:06:46,539
You're smart, and you cook well.

86
00:06:46,539 --> 00:06:47,540
The Gu Jin I know

87
00:06:47,540 --> 00:06:49,876
