105
00:07:49,969 --> 00:07:51,637
But even if you can't bear it alone,

106
00:07:51,637 --> 00:07:53,840
I can bear it with you.

107
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:55,208
You?

108
00:07:56,142 --> 00:07:57,856
With what?

109
00:07:58,411 --> 00:08:00,512
Fine. I might not be able to,

110
00:08:01,547 --> 00:08:03,516
but I can be your battery.

111
00:08:04,417 --> 00:08:06,285
Come to me when you're tired,

112
00:08:06,285 --> 00:08:08,032
and I can recharge you.

113
00:08:09,388 --> 00:08:11,840
I don't want you to bear all this alone.

114
00:08:23,135 --> 00:08:24,504
You know?

115
00:08:25,671 --> 00:08:28,508
When the bluebird is not needed,

116
00:08:29,175 --> 00:08:32,256
