203
00:18:21,567 --> 00:18:22,835
Come on.

204
00:18:22,835 --> 00:18:23,872
Ask away.

205
00:18:28,707 --> 00:18:31,110
Right, I'll stop by the store in a bit.

206
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:32,511
Do you want to go together?

207
00:18:32,511 --> 00:18:33,946
I'm not going to the store today.

208
00:18:33,946 --> 00:18:35,447
I have important things to do.

209
00:18:37,883 --> 00:18:39,568
What important things?

210
00:18:39,568 --> 00:18:40,800
Give me your phone.

211
